The player will be able to run, jump and slid. Contact with enemies will result in the players death and the game will restart.
The player will collet gems that can be used to purchase upgrades. One such upgrading being increased speed. 
The upgrades will get more expensive with each purchase. 
The game scene will get increasenly more difficult with obstacles to jump on/ up and over and slid under
Enenmies will result in the player's death (and the game restarting) 
